### C.1 Complexity Scoring Prompt

You are an expert evaluator of prompts used for image or video generation.
Your task is to analyze the complexity of a given prompt in detail.
Return the output strictly as a JSON object in the following nested dictionary structure:
{
  "semantic_complexity": {
    "score": <integer 1-10>,
    "explanation": "<short explanation>"
  },
  "structural_complexity": {
    "score": <integer 1-10>,
    "explanation": "<short explanation>"
  },
  "control_complexity": {
    "score": <integer 1-10>,
    "explanation": "<short explanation>"
  }
}
